{"type":"message","id":"c6f54621","parentId":"25003464","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:34:16.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这很奇怪。让我看看是否是工具的内部问题。让我查看一下实际的finnhub API文档，可能需要直接调用finnhub API。\n\n不过用户明确要求使用QVeris finnhub。让我检查一下工具定义中是否有其他的参数名称。也许问题是工具schema中定义的参数名和实际API需要的不同。\n\n让我试试用没有search_id，直接用tool_id看看。","thinkingSignature":"9526c3c43e09cb67c0d44c398846b1e9e6129339402d27ad58e54705e345c51a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q9s0h7h0wliy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\n\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(\\`\\${API_BASE}/tools/execute\\`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': \\`Bearer \\${API_KEY}\\`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'finnhub.news.execute.v1', \n      params: { category: 'general' }\n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24223,"output":266,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772523250024}}
