urceFeed\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"exactCategoryMatch\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"If set to true, the api will return stories with only the requested category\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"xml\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"format\": \"json\",\n          \"displayType\": \"headline\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Barchart OnDemand's market data APIs let you power your apps, websites and software with financial market data and information directly from exchanges around the world. Maintained through Amazon Web Services, Barchart OnDemand APIs are flexible and can be delivered in multiple formats including XML, JSON and CSV, and can be streamed over websockets.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.market.news.list.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get latest market news.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"News category. Available values: \\\\`general\\\\` \\\\`forex\\\\` \\\\`crypto\\\\` \\\\`merger\\\\`\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"general\",\n            \"forex\",\n            \"crypto\",\n            \"merger\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1.874,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"222a2cce-105d-4e0e-ad3a-c0831a2b0e64\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 690.84\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5573,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"fmp articles financial news\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.fmp_articles.list.v1.2df51706\",\n      \"name\": \"FMP Articles API\",\n      \"description\": \"Access the latest general news articles from a variety of sources with the FMP General News API. Obtain headlines, snippets, and publication URLs for comprehensive news coverage.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"page\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Page number like 0\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit like 20\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1148.1,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.685\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"yahoo_finance.finance_news.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Yahoo Finance News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get financial news and articles for stocks and companies\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol to get news for (optional, uses general finance news if not provided)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"max_results\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Maximum number of news articles to return (default: 10)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"news_type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Type of news to retrieve\",\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"all\",\n            \"headlines\",\n            \"detailed\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_range\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Time range for news articles\",\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"1d\",\n            \"7d\",\n            \"30d\",\n            \"90d\",\n            \"1y\",\n            \"all\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Yahoo Finance data provider using yfinance SDK for stock market data, news, and financial information\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Financial News\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns the latest financial news headlines and full articles for a given ticker symbol or topic tag. Requires either a ticker (s) or a tag (t). Supports filtering by date, pagination, and JSON response format.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The ticker code to retrieve news for, for example: AAPL.US\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"t\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The topic tag to retrieve news for, for example: technology\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering news (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Number of results to return (default: 50, minimum: 1, maximum: 1000)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"offset\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Offset for pagination (default: 0)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format, either json or xml (default: json)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {}\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1.183,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.741\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_finance.finance_news_aggregation_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Finance News Aggregation\",\n      \"description\": \"Search and aggregate financial news from multiple sources\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query for financial news\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Provider for finance-related skills\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"aggregation\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.2e72ea5d\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get latest market news.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"minId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.51b2567e\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get latest market news.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"minId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 2.911,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get latest market news.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"minId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 807.31,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.997\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.financials.list.v2.e2500a07\",\n      \"name\": \"List Financials\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve a collection of financial posts.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"context\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Scope under which the request is made; determines fields present in response.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"view\",\n            \"embed\",\n            \"edit\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"page\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Current page of the collection.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"per_page\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of items to be returned in result set.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"search\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit results to those matching a string.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"after\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit response to posts published after a given ISO8601 compliant date.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"modified_after\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit response to posts modified after a given ISO8601 compliant date.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"before\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit response to posts published before a given ISO8601 compliant date.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"modified_before\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit response to posts modified before a given ISO8601 compliant date.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"exclude\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ensure result set excludes specific IDs.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"include\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit result set to specific IDs.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"search_semantics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"How to interpret the search input.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"exact\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"offset\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Offset the result set by a specific number of items.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"order\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Order sort attribute ascending or descending.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"asc\",\n            \"desc\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"orderby\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sort collection by post attribute.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"author\",\n            \"date\",\n            \"id\",\n            \"include\",\n            \"modified\",\n            \"parent\",\n            \"relevance\",\n            \"slug\",\n            \"include_slugs\",\n            \"title\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"search_columns\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Array of column names to be searched.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"slug\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit result set to posts with one or more specific slugs.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"status\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Limit result set to posts assigned one or more statuses.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"barchart.ondemand.news.query.v1.655e0a3e\",\n      \"name\": \"Query News Articles\",\n      \"description\": \"The getNews API returns news headlines, articles and related photos based upon news sources, category, sub-category and/or keyword. With this API you can access breaking news, company press releases and global financial market coverage.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sources\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news feed code\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AP\",\n            \"APAI\",\n            \"BC\",\n            \"BCNEWS\",\n            \"CP\",\n            \"CNW\",\n            \"CRB\",\n            \"CMTX\",\n            \"CMTX:PCS\",\n            \"CMTX:PCC\",\n            \"CMTX:SEC\",\n            \"IF\",\n            \"USDA\",\n            \"PRNW\",\n            \"ZACKS\",\n            \"BRUG\",\n            \"AGWEB\",\n            \"SETZ\",\n            \"SPC\",\n            \"NASS\",\n            \"ESTMZ\",\n            \"DVND\",\n            \"LME-WHS\",\n            \"DLFRX\",\n            \"GLDRPT\",\n            \"COT\",\n            \"MAX\",\n            \"CMDTY_AGLITE\",\n            \"CMDTY_AG\",\n            \"CMDTY_ENERGY\",\n            \"SYNDTGAM\",\n            \"FCTGAM\",\n            \"BCSYND\",\n            \"HDLNE\",\n            \"HDLNEG\",\n            \"HDLNEP\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbols\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A symbol or code that identifies a financial instrument\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A grouping of related news content\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"companies\",\n            \"politics\",\n            \"geography\",\n            \"commodities\",\n            \"economics\",\n            \"stocks\",\n            \"futures\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"subCategory\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A more specific category of related news content\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"private companies\",\n            \"stock equities\",\n            \"stock trading\",\n            \"stock options\",\n            \"regulatory\",\n            \"corporate events\",\n            \"analyst ratings\",\n            \"industries\",\n            \"mergers & acquisitions\",\n            \"employees\",\n            \"financials\",\n            \"consumer discretionary\",\n            \"health care\",\n            \"private equity\",\n            \"management\",\n            \"technology\",\n            \"financing\",\n            \"partnership\",\n            \"shareholder voting\",\n            \"media & telecom\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"industrials\",\n            \"energy\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"technical analysis\",\n            \"real estate\",\n            \"insider transaction\",\n            \"utilities\",\n            \"consumer staples\",\n            \"dividends\",\n            \"analyst downgrade\",\n            \"bankruptcies & insolvencies\",\n            \"venture capital\",\n            \"analyst upgrade\",\n            \"materials\",\n            \"elections\",\n            \"law\",\n            \"taxes\",\n            \"iraq\",\n            \"asia\",\n            \"s. korea\",\n            \"spain\",\n            \"russia\",\n            \"china\",\n            \"philippines\",\n            \"chile\",\n            \"peru\",\n            \"united states\",\n            \"australia\",\n            \"bolivia\",\n            \"united kingdom\",\n            \"europe\",\n            \"canada\",\n            \"japan\",\n            \"mexico\",\n            \"germany\",\n            \"france\",\n            \"brazil\",\n            \"new zealand\",\n            \"singapore\",\n            \"cuba\",\n            \"argentina\",\n            \"en\",\n            \"equity index\",\n            \"agriculture\",\n            \"grain\",\n            \"futures education\",\n            \"options on futures\",\n            \"futures exchange\",\n            \"food & beverage\",\n            \"interest rates\",\n            \"cryptocurrencies\",\n            \"top news\",\n            \"lumber\",\n            \"forex\",\n            \"weather\",\n            \"metals\",\n            \"fruits & vegetables\",\n            \"softs\",\n            \"livestock\",\n            \"ethanol\",\n            \"soybean\",\n            \"coffee\",\n            \"canola\",\n            \"renewable energy\",\n            \"hogs\",\n            \"rubber\",\n            \"e-waste\",\n            \"lamb\",\n            \"batteries\",\n            \"nuts\",\n            \"gold\",\n            \"ferrous metals\",\n            \"rice\",\n            \"sugar\",\n            \"fruits\",\n            \"cocoa\",\n            \"silver\",\n            \"corn\",\n            \"steel\",\n            \"poultry\",\n            \"heating oil\",\n            \"fertilizer\",\n            \"cattle\",\n            \"copper\",\n            \"sorghum\",\n            \"crude oil\",\n            \"scrap metal\",\n            \"coal\",\n            \"cotton\",\n            \"vegetables\",\n            \"wheat\",\n            \"corporate debt\",\n            \"natural gas\",\n            \"gasoil\",\n            \"non-ferrous metals\",\n            \"dairy\",\n            \"global trade\",\n            \"employment\",\n            \"central banks\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"series\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A grouping of stories under a recurring news topic\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"MORNCALL\",\n            \"COD\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"keyword\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A term used to create searches\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"maxRecords\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The maximum number of records to show in the return\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"startDate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The beginning date for the query in ISO 8601 format\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"displayType\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The type of news displayed: headlines only, headline and preview, or full\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"headline\",\n            \"preview\",\n            \"full\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"images\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"An option for returning the images contained in the news article\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"storyId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Parameter allows to get specific story by providing newsID\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rss\",\n          \"type\": \"boolean\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Parameter formats XML requests as RSS feeds\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"rssTitle\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Parameter overrides the default RSS feed title and description\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fields\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The additional fields requested\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"barchartClassification\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Classify stories in some categories\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"organization\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news organization that