{"type":"message","id":"9c44ebfd","parentId":"a94416e8","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:36:09.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我注意到Alpha Vantage的工具成功率是0.973（非常接近1），而finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.2e72ea5d成功率是未定义的。让我试试finnhub.market.news.list.v1，这个有成功率1。让我执行这个试试。","thinkingSignature":"eaed3d5e64588e4219b7112c71696b235ed981e3ce7db275f0892d0c2eaddd5a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zbjux6zwrq5o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\n\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(\\`\\${API_BASE}/tools/execute\\`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': \\`Bearer \\${API_KEY}\\`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'finnhub.market.news.list.v1', \n      search_id: 'd6ed8c06-de83-42bf-9bd3-23b3fb7e124d',\n      params: { category: 'general' }\n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":35699,"output":277,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49960,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772523361914}}
