{"type":"message","id":"5c139f6a","parentId":"0b98dad4","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:36:35.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Finnhub API需要有效的API key，demo key无效。QVeris工具应该是使用自己的API key。让我再次检查是否有其他替代方案。让我搜索看看是否有其他新闻API带有热度分数，并且可以在QVeris上工作。","thinkingSignature":"8d2b847e61c521ab84607f44bdbb092e38fb38cc597618a2acafaf43ca6a6fe8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dyp57kszcm7y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"news sentiment relevance score hot trending\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36754,"output":106,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772523390931}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9eff197","parentId":"5c139f6a","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:36:38.358Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dyp57kszcm7y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"news sentiment relevance score hot trending\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"s\": \"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1278.53,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 520.43,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.987\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Topics Tracker\",\n      \"description\": \"Track and aggregate hot topics from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter platform. Supports multiple domains: AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"List of domains to query. Available: AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science. If not specified, queries all domains.\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域列表。可选：AI、Finance、Crypto、Tech、Science。如不指定则查询所有领域。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return per domain\",\n            \"zh\": \"每个领域返回结果的最大数量\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"min_engagement\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Minimum engagement (likes + retweets + replies) for filtering posts\",\n            \"zh\": \"用于过滤的最小互动量（点赞+转发+回复）\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_account_hottest_post_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Account Hottest Post (7 Days)\",\n      \"description\": \"Return the single hottest post (by engagement) from a given X/Twitter account in the last 7 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"username\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"X/Twitter username (without @)\",\n            \"zh\": \"X账号用户名（不含@）\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"account\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Alias for username\",\n            \"zh\": \"同 username\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_account_hottest_post_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"x_developer.2.trends.by.woeid.retrieve.v2.21f95686\",\n      \"name\": \"Get Trends by WOEID\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieves trending topics for a specific location identified by its WOEID.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"woeid\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The WOEID of the place to lookup a trend for.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"max_trends\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The maximum number of results.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"trend.fields\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A comma separated list of Trend fields to display.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"woeid\": 1\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Use X API to fetch posts, users, trends, etc.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 744.33,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.302\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Events Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Summarize today's hot events on X/Twitter for a domain: fetch new posts then use LLM to summarize events and return event list with post ids.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domain(s) to summarize\",\n            \"zh\": \"要总结的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.tonechart.retrieve.v2.a7b24341\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Tone Chart\",\n      \"description\": \"Generates a histogram showing the distribution of article tones (from extremely negative to extremely positive) for articles mentioning a specific query over the last 3 months.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query phrase\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API operation mode\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"tonechart\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"tonechart\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 19242.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.077\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain New Posts Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Search today's new posts from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter with full fields: text, images, media, metrics. Supports AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domains to query\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": null\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\n      \"description\": \"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 883.34,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"fdc4df1e-20fe-44fb-802e-23164a67c89e\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 631.09\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2631,"aggregated":"{\n  \"query\": \"news sentiment relevance score hot trending\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\n      \"description\": \"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"s\": \"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1278.53,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 520.43,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.987\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Topics Tracker\",\n      \"description\": \"Track and aggregate hot topics from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter platform. Supports multiple domains: AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"List of domains to query. Available: AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science. If not specified, queries all domains.\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域列表。可选：AI、Finance、Crypto、Tech、Science。如不指定则查询所有领域。\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results to return per domain\",\n            \"zh\": \"每个领域返回结果的最大数量\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"min_engagement\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Minimum engagement (likes + retweets + replies) for filtering posts\",\n            \"zh\": \"用于过滤的最小互动量（点赞+转发+回复）\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_account_hottest_post_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Account Hottest Post (7 Days)\",\n      \"description\": \"Return the single hottest post (by engagement) from a given X/Twitter account in the last 7 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"username\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"X/Twitter username (without @)\",\n            \"zh\": \"X账号用户名（不含@）\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"account\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Alias for username\",\n            \"zh\": \"同 username\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_account_hottest_post_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"x_developer.2.trends.by.woeid.retrieve.v2.21f95686\",\n      \"name\": \"Get Trends by WOEID\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieves trending topics for a specific location identified by its WOEID.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"woeid\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The WOEID of the place to lookup a trend for.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"max_trends\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The maximum number of results.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"trend.fields\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"A comma separated list of Trend fields to display.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"woeid\": 1\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Use X API to fetch posts, users, trends, etc.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 744.33,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.302\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Events Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Summarize today's hot events on X/Twitter for a domain: fetch new posts then use LLM to summarize events and return event list with post ids.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domain(s) to summarize\",\n            \"zh\": \"要总结的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.tonechart.retrieve.v2.a7b24341\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Tone Chart\",\n      \"description\": \"Generates a histogram showing the distribution of article tones (from extremely negative to extremely positive) for articles mentioning a specific query over the last 3 months.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query phrase\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API operation mode\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"tonechart\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"tonechart\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 19242.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.077\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain New Posts Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Search today's new posts from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter with full fields: text, images, media, metrics. Supports AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domains to query\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": null\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\n      \"description\": \"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 883.34,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"fdc4df1e-20fe-44fb-802e-23164a67c89e\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 631.09\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772523398354}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa1b09d1","parentId":"e9eff197","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:36:58.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现了一个有趣的选项：qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1 可以跟踪X/Twitter上的热门话题。它支持\"Finance\"领域，并且有min_engagement参数来筛选热度。这个可能可以作为\"热度\"的替代。\n\n但用户明确要求使用Finnhub财经新闻，并且热度>=80。这个\"热度\"应该是指Alpha Vantage的relevance_score字段（0-100的范围）。\n\n让我再试一下看看是否有办法绕过这个参数传递问题。也许我可以用不同的search_id来调用。\n\n让我用search后返回的search_id直接调用。","thinkingSignature":"b0a22be134fa654e4b022fb1d20abed15f344b850665ce7d7d0d78d62f1476cd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7313rfn2b2a0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\n\n// Try with search_id from the search results\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(\\`\\${API_BASE}/tools/execute\\`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': \\`Bearer \\${API_KEY}\\`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0',\n      search_id: 'fdc4df1e-20fe-44fb-802e-23164a67c89e',\n      params: { function: 'NEWS_SENTIMENT', sort: 'RELEVANCE', limit: 50 }\n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38492,"output":363,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772523398359}}
