{"type":"message","id":"f2491e2c","parentId":"2476444f","timestamp":"2026-03-03T07:37:12.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个方法也不行。这是一个系统性的问题。让我尝试另一种方法——直接用空params看看能不能获取到默认的新闻。\n\n实际上，考虑到Finnhub工具的参数问题，我现在有几个选择：\n\n1. 告知用户Finnhub工具在QVeris上有bug\n2. 尝试使用FMP新闻（可以工作但没有热度分数）\n3. 尝试使用X Domain Hot Topics（可以作为热度参考）\n\n让我尝试一下qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1，虽然它不是Finnhub，但可以作为获取热门财经话题的替代方案。这个至少可以工作。","thinkingSignature":"24cfcc7f163d85c0815758cd584f04593b3c80e39128a78c9cd70021bf918a88"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uj0k1y1owk6v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\n\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(\\`\\${API_BASE}/tools/execute\\`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': \\`Bearer \\${API_KEY}\\`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'qveris_social.x_domain_hot_topics_v1',\n      params: { domains: ['Finance'], limit: 30, min_engagement: 80 }\n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38982,"output":319,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772523419266}}
